<plot>"Heather " is a high school drama that follows teenager, Heather, an outsider who tries to get closer to popular boy Steve, who she thinks might have feelings for her. Heather sneaks into Steve's weekend party and he rapes her. Heather must again defend herself when Jenny, Steve's girlfriend, accosts her at school. In the end, Heather must decide to either agree to her Parents' terms to avoid the problem and say that it never happened or take the matter into her own hands.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?233594</url></doc>
